snippet: The owners of the M. Wells Dinette, which recently opened at the MoMA PS1, said they were surprised by the vehement reaction to their intended menu offering.
lead_paragraph: The owners of the M. Wells Dinette, which recently opened at the MoMA PS1, said they were surprised by the vehement reaction to their intended menu offering.

headline.seo: M. Wells Dinette Will Not Sell Horse Meat, Owners Say
headline.main: Outcry Scuttles Plan to Put Horse on a New York Menu
